sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(Gateway/Route)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as MLServer REST API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC API<br/>8081/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(SKLearn/XGBoost/LightGBM/ONNX)
    participant FS as Filesystem<br/>(/mnt/models)
    participant Allowlist as Trusted Runtimes<br/>(/etc/mlserver/trusted-runtimes.json)
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Client, Runtime: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Ingress->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>TLS (8443/TCP)
    KRBAC->>REST: HTTP (8080/TCP)<br/>localhost/pod network
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Runtime: Dispatch inference<br/>Trusted runtimes validated
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>KRBAC: HTTP response
    KRBAC-->>Ingress: TLS response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Client, Runtime: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Ingress: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Ingress->>GRPC: gRPC/HTTP2 (8081/TCP)<br/>Pod network
    GRPC->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Runtime: Dispatch inference
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>GRPC: gRPC response
    GRPC-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Kafka, Runtime: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference (Optional)

    Kafka-->>DP: Consume from input topic<br/>9092/TCP Kafka protocol
    DP->>Runtime: Dispatch inference
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP->>Kafka: Produce to output topic<br/>9092/TCP Kafka protocol

    Note over FS, Allowlist: Flow 4: Model Loading at Startup

    FS-->>DP: Read model-settings.json<br/>from /mnt/models
    DP->>Allowlist: Validate implementation<br/>against trusted-runtimes.json
    Allowlist-->>DP: Approved / Rejected
    DP->>Runtime: Import and initialize model<br/>(only pre-installed packages)
